# direnv config for the-unnecessary novel project.
#
# Loads environment variables from .env (gitignored) into the shell so that
# tools launched from this directory, including Claude Code MCP servers that
# use ${VAR} expansion in .mcp.json (e.g. ELEVENLABS_API_KEY), can resolve them.
#
# Keep real secrets ONLY in .env, never in this file. This file is safe to commit
# because it contains no secrets, only the directive to load .env.
#
# After editing: run `direnv allow` once, then restart Claude Code so the running
# process inherits the exported variables.

dotenv
